"Hay\u0131r, o alevlenen bir ate\u015ftir."}, {"id": 585183, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5391, "text": "Derileri kavurur, soyar."}, {"id": 585184, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5392, "text": "\u00c7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131r, s\u0131rt\u0131n\u0131 d\u00f6n\u00fcp gideni,"}, {"id": 585185, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 227, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5393, "text": "Mal toplay\u0131p kasada y\u0131\u011fan\u0131,"}, {"id": 585186, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5394, "text": "Do\u011frusu insan dayan\u0131ks\u0131z ve huysuz yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r."}, {"id": 585187, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5395, "text": "Kendisine k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fck dokundu mu s\u0131zlan\u0131r."}, {"id": 585188, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5396, "text": "Kendisine hay\u0131r dokundu mu cimrilik eder."}, {"id": 585189, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5397, "text": "Ancak namaz k\u0131lanlar bunun d\u0131\u015f\u0131ndad\u0131r."}, {"id": 585190, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5398, "text": "Onlar ki namazlar\u0131n\u0131 s\u00fcrekli k\u0131larlar."}, {"id": 585191, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5399, "text": "Onlar\u0131n mallar\u0131nda belli bir hak vard\u0131r,"}, {"id": 585192, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5400, "text": "Hem isteyen i\u00e7in, hem de istemekten utanan yoksul i\u00e7in."}, {"id": 585193, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5401, "text": "Onlar ki ceza g\u00fcn\u00fcn\u00fc tasdik ederler."}, {"id": 585194, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5402, "text": "Rablerinin azab\u0131ndan korkarlar."}, {"id": 585195, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5403, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Rablerinin azab\u0131ndan emin olunmaz."}, {"id": 585196, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5404, "text": "Onlar ki \u0131rzlar\u0131n\u0131 korurlar."}, {"id": 585197, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5405, "text": "Ancak zevcelerine ve cariyelerine kar\u015f\u0131 hari\u00e7. \u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc onlara yakla\u015ft\u0131klar\u0131nda k\u0131nanmazlar."}, {"id": 585198, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5406, "text": "Bundan \u00f6tesini isteyenler, var ya i\u015fte onlar haddi a\u015fanlard\u0131r."}, {"id": 585199, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5407, "text": "Onlar emanetlerini ve ahitlerini g\u00f6zetirler."}, {"id": 585200, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5408, "text": "\u015eahitliklerinde d\u00fcr\u00fcstt\u00fcrler."}, {"id": 585201, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5409, "text": "Namazlar\u0131na devam ederler."}, {"id": 585202, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 502, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5410, "text": "\u0130\u015fte bunlar cennetlerde a\u011f\u0131rlan\u0131rlar."}, {"id": 585203, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5411, "text": "\u015eimdi ne oluyor o ink\u00e2r edenlere ki, sana do\u011fru boyunlar\u0131n\u0131 uzatarak ko\u015fuyorlar:"}, {"id": 585204, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5412, "text": "Sa\u011fdan ve soldan b\u00f6l\u00fck b\u00f6l\u00fck."}, {"id": 585205, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5413, "text": "Onlardan herbiri, bir nimet cennetine sokulaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 m\u0131 umuyor?"}, {"id": 585206, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 569, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5414, "text": "Hay\u0131r, biz onlar\u0131 bildikleri \u015feyden yaratt\u0131k."}, {"id": 585207, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5415, "text": "Art\u0131k o do\u011fular\u0131n ve bat\u0131lar\u0131n Rabbine yemine ne gerek, elbette bizim g\u00fcc\u00fcm\u00fcz yeter."}, {"id": 585208, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5416, "text": "Onlar\u0131 kendilerinden daha hay\u0131rl\u0131 olanlarla de\u011fi\u015ftirebiliriz ve bizim \u00f6n\u00fcm\u00fcze ge\u00e7ilmez."}, {"id": 585209, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5417, "text": "O halde b\u0131rak onlar\u0131, kendilerine vaad edilen g\u00fcnlerine kavu\u015funcaya kadar dal\u0131p oynayadursunlar."}, {"id": 585210, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5418, "text": "O g\u00fcn kabirlerden h\u0131zl\u0131 h\u0131zl\u0131 \u00e7\u0131kacaklar, sanki putlara gidiyorlarm\u0131\u015f gibi f\u0131rlayacaklar."}, {"id": 585211, "identifier": "tr.yazir", "surah_number": 70, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0639\u0627\u0631\u062c", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ma'aarij", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Ascending Stairways", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 570, "ruku": 503, "hizb_quarter": 228, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Elmal\u0131l\u0131 Hamdi Yaz\u0131r", "transelator_en_name": "Elmalili Hamdi Yazir", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5419, "text": "G\u00f6zleri d\u00fc\u015f\u00fck, kendilerini bir al\u00e7akl\u0131k saracak da saracak. \u0130\u015fte onlara vaad edilen g\u00fcn, o g\u00fcnd\u00fcr."}]